name: John Tyler
description: I’m a military officer, I’m a fun loving man that has caring and compassion to share with that special someone. I have a lot to offer to that lady. I believe in honesty and trust and i’m very dedicated and will stand by her for the rest of my life. I want to show her what happiness really is and to fulfill her life with joy and all the love possible! I believe in being kind. I can strike up conversations with those I don’t even know. I’m always smiling. hugging someone, I’m compassionate, fun, loving. I believe in spreading “happiness and smiles” with a butter knife. Every day is significant, not just holidays. Giving to those I care about is very important to me.
